defs.name: EtherscanError
defs.value:
enum EtherscanError {
    ChainNotSupported(Chain),
    ExecutionFailed(String),
    BalanceFailed,
    TransactionReceiptFailed,
    GasEstimationFailed,
    BadStatusCode(String),
    EnvVarNotFound(VarError),
    Reqwest(reqwest::Error),
    Serde(serde_json::Error),
    ContractCodeNotVerified(Address),
    RateLimitExceeded,
    IO(std::io::Error),
    LocalNetworksNotSupported,
    Unknown(String),
    Builder(String),
    MissingSolcVersion(String),
    InvalidApiKey,
    BlockedByCloudflare,
}

 - New field `gasUsedRatio`, to estimate how busy the network is
